CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 2, 1961, pg. 20 reads: "Races And Games Winners show appreciation and prizes. Awards were given to all age groups."
TitMainTitle: Group of young men and boys holding basketballs, footballs, and flashlights, gathered on field in South Park for annual Pittsburgh Courier Newsboys' Picnic
